SIMPLE: mechoacan
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mechoacan
<hw>Me*cho"a*can</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A species of
jalap, of very feeble properties, said to be obtained from the root of a
species of <gen>Convolvulus</gen> (<spn>Convolvulus Mechoacan</spn>); --
so called from <etsep>Michoacan</etsep>, in Mexico, whence it is
obtained.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Meckelian</ent>⟦br⟧
